rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0004
rows.name:
Even if you are the safety device,
if I eradicate you while you are just wooden dolls![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0005
rows.name: Notification from Central Life Control System.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0006
rows.name:
This unit is being exposed to attacks from hostile action.
Initiating internal defense system now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0007
rows.name:
That brain-guy...
Does he intend to destroy the control system!?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0009
rows.name: Do not speak my name so lightly![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0010
rows.name:
Do you intend to say that we are the cancer cells!?
I won't let us be destroyed![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0011
rows.name:
Everyone, stop him!
At this rate, the control system will...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0017
rows.name:
The system that cultivates immigrants from Earth
doubles as a defense mechanism that creates biological weapons.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0019
rows.name:
Such[ST:wide ]— Such monsters
are the defense mechanism[ST:wide ]—?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0020
rows.name:
The system is running wild.
We have to stop it quickly![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0022
rows.name: It has an ugly form, just like you Earthlings![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0023
rows.name: I don't want to hear that from you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12120100_MSG0027
rows.name:
Leave this guy to me!
You guys stop the defense system![ST:wait ]
